    <section class="highlight">
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="highlight-text">
          <p>We conduct research to improve the sustainability of livestock production in arid rangelands as well as the sustainability of supply chains connected to Southwestern U.S. livestock production. More generally, this research is developing novel approaches to quantify the synergies and tradeoffs of multiple sustainability indicators in agricultural systems as well as the flows of costs and benefits through agricultural supply chains.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
